                edit ~/.config/easyprint.conf (printer uri, paper size)
                ----------
                Usage example:
                $ ep into_the_core.pdf
                ----------
                Notes:
                * pdf and image files are supported by default
                * libreoffice is needed to print office files
                * yad is needed if you want a gui in X
                * yad and appindicator-broker are needed if you want a gui in wayland
                * for more details: $ ep --help
